  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::History
  _text: {fileID: 1343124155}
  _fadeAnimation: {fileID: 1343124157}
  _pages:
  - Year 19XX - Military Curfew
  - The armed forces have taken control of the country following a coup against the
    president.
  - All imports have been completely banned and possession of any foreign product
    is punishable by law.
  - I've seen many restaurants like mine fall apart.
  - I am one of the last ones left...
  - One of the last ones willing to cook what people truly want.
  - And I will cook...
  - ...until their last bite.
  _pageTime: 6
